Class SessionProxy

java.lang.Object
  vista.set.Session
      vista.set.SessionProxy
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, GroupManager, Named
public abstract class SessionProxy
extends Session

A proxy for this session which loads the groups only when operations other than setName() and getName() are requested.
